    public static enum MicrometerMeterListenerDocumentation.TerminationTags
extends java.lang.Enum<MicrometerMeterListenerDocumentation.TerminationTags>
implements io.micrometer.common.docs.KeyName
    Additional tags for PublisherMeters#FLOW_DURATION that reflects the termination of the sequence.

    • 枚举常量概要

      枚举常量 
      枚举常量和说明
      EXCEPTION
      Tag used by FLOW_DURATION when STATUS is "error", to store the exception that occurred.
      STATUS
      The termination status: "completed" for a sequence that terminates with an onComplete, with onNext(s) "completedEmpty" for a sequence that terminates without any onNext before the onComplete "error" for a sequence that terminates with an onError "cancelled" for a sequence that has cancelled its subscription

    • 枚举常量详细资料

      • STATUS

        public static final MicrometerMeterListenerDocumentation.TerminationTags STATUS
        The termination status:
        • "completed" for a sequence that terminates with an onComplete, with onNext(s)
        • "completedEmpty" for a sequence that terminates without any onNext before the onComplete
        • "error" for a sequence that terminates with an onError
        • "cancelled" for a sequence that has cancelled its subscription

      • EXCEPTION

        public static final MicrometerMeterListenerDocumentation.TerminationTags EXCEPTION
        Tag used by FLOW_DURATION when STATUS is "error", to store the exception that occurred.
